she devised a scheme

16
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:53,680
to convince my father

17
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,240
to send me away,

18
00:01:55,450 --> 00:01:56,370
just like that.

19
00:01:57,110 --> 00:01:57,950
(In the past,)

20
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,490
