(he shared a fate similar to mine,)

25
00:02:06,730 --> 00:02:07,570
(branded an ill omen)

26
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,240
(from our birth.)

27
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:10,560
But what if that fortune-teller

28
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,770
was a fraud,

29
00:02:11,930 --> 00:02:13,400
spouting doom just to

30
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,400
seek fame and fortune?

31
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,960
So what if he's a fraud?

32
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,160
There's no point

33
00:02:19,160 --> 00:02:20,280
in digging deeper now.

34
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,090
Ultimately,

35
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:24,800
the decision

36
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,840
lies with our parents.

37
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:29,890
You think it's pointless,

38
00:02:30,050 --> 00:02:31,050
but I think

39
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,680
it is necessary.

40
00:02:33,050 --> 00:02:34,250
If the vulnerable

41
00:02:34,250 --> 00:02:35,050
are saddled

42
