with all sorts of false charges

43
00:02:36,090 --> 00:02:37,240
by people in the world

44
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,600
without question

45
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:39,720
or resistance,

46
00:02:40,090 --> 00:02:41,090
doesn't that

47
00:02:41,090 --> 00:02:42,330
validate the wicked's lies

48
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,050
and make themselves accomplices?

49
