after all these years,

57
00:03:07,940 --> 00:03:09,340
don't you want to know the truth?

58
00:03:10,060 --> 00:03:11,500
One Capital Security Office,

59
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:13,140
two people giving me a headache.

60
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:19,620
But who reported the buried bodies

61
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:21,460
at the Marquis's Mansion?

62
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:22,620
It was the fourth daughter

63
00:03:22,780 --> 00:03:24,460
of Earl Dongping's household,

64
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:25,740
Jiang Si.

65
00:03:26,340 --> 00:03:27,180
Cao Xingyu

66
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,460
is her second sister's husband.

67
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:31,000
That day,

68
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,300
the second daughter of the Jiang Family

69
00:03:32,300 --> 00:03:33,740
invited her sisters to

70
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:34,740
the Marquis's Mansion.

71
