and stumbled upon servants burying a body.

74
00:03:41,940 --> 00:03:42,940
She reported it

75
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:43,940
to the Capital Security.

76
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:46,020
But later,

77
00:03:46,180 --> 00:03:47,900
Cao Xingyu, the villain, struck first,

78
