90
00:04:12,660 --> 00:04:13,500
Your Highness,

91
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,300
the Speed Guards

92
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:16,420
have mentioned Cao Xingyu

93
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:18,060
