Your son kneels in contrition, Father.

122
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:33,540
The 1st and 3rd Princes are here!

123
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,740
The 5th Prince is here!

124
00:05:37,300 --> 00:05:40,100
The 6th and 8th Princes are here!

125
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:45,860
Your sons kneel in contrition, Father.

126
00:05:47,340 --> 00:05:48,660
Why did you come so late

127
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:49,900
to kneel in contrition?

128
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:54,180
(Yu Lang, Crown Prince)
Father, though I had

129
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:56,300
a few encounters with Marquis Changxing's,

130
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:57,300
no, Cao Xingyu, the criminal,

131
00:05:57,660 --> 00:05:59,460
our acquaintance was merely superficial.

132
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:00,900
I truly had no knowledge

133
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,660
of his murderous deeds.

134
00:06:02,980 --> 00:06:04,780
Father, Marquis Changxing has been

135
