(Yu Zhang, Prince Qi)
at odds with me,

136
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:08,660
but Ling'an hasn't witnessed

137
00:06:08,660 --> 00:06:10,980
such a heinous murder in decades.

138
00:06:11,540 --> 00:06:12,980
Your personal trial of Cao Xingyu

139
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,660
has been universally praised by the people.

140
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,420
Father is wise.

141
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:18,900
Father is wise.

142
