143
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:24,060
for Cao Xingyu's case.

144
00:06:27,060 --> 00:06:28,180
All right, all rise.

145
00:06:28,180 --> 00:06:29,540
Thank you, Father.

146
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:37,300
Since you're all here,

147
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:38,860
I'd like to ask you

148
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:40,780
if you think

149
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:42,500
I'm usually

150
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:43,900
too strict with you.

151
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:52,780
Yu Lang, you tell me.

152
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:55,620
Father,

153
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:56,980
