169
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:31,660
I don't have much energy

170
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:33,780
to teach most of you.

171
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:34,900
Of course,

172
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:37,980
Yu Lang is the crown prince.

173
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:40,340
I'm naturally more strict with him.

174
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:41,500
If you have

175
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,740
anything to say,

176
00:07:42,740 --> 00:07:44,740
speak freely tonight.

177
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:46,980
Don't hold it back.

178
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:49,740
People holding their feelings in for too long

179
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:51,780
will inevitably lose their rationality

180
00:07:52,300 --> 00:07:53,460
and come up with devious ways

181
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:55,980
to relieve their emotions.

182
00:07:56,420 --> 00:07:57,340
Do you understand?

183
00:07:58,180 --> 00:08:00,660
We will follow your instructions.

184
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:06,220
