know that Zhang and I are innocent.

190
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:43,260
Do not penalize us

191
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:47,500
because of Qi.

192
00:08:47,780 --> 00:08:49,300
The ministers say

193
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:52,660
he brought disaster to Dazhou.

194
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,820
Then send him away,

195
00:08:57,540 --> 00:08:59,300
(Consort Xian, Yu Qi's birth mother)
away from

196
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:02,300
the Imperial City and Dazhou.

197
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:05,420
Qi is the child you carried for ten months.

198
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:07,300
Can you bear to part with him?

199
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:10,780
Even if I can't, what can I do?

200
00:09:11,660 --> 00:09:12,780
He was fated

201
00:09:12,780 --> 00:09:15,300
with ill omen from his first breath.

202
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,500
Qi was sent to the South

203
00:09:21,660 --> 00:09:23,540
in swaddling clothes.

204
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:26,020
Left on the war-torn frontiers

205
00:09:26,420 --> 00:09:28,540
to grow up alone without his parents,

206
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:31,580
who knows what he's become.

207
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:34,020
The boy is wayward.

208
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:37,060
Every time Cui Xu went on an inspection tour,

209
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:39,300
I sent him to check on him,

210
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:42,660
but he always avoided meeting him.

211
00:09:42,940 --> 00:09:45,420
He must hold a grudge against me.

212
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:46,620
Your Majesty,

213
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:49,020
if you miss the 7th Prince,

214
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:51,420
why not summon him back to Ling'an?

215
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:53,380
The Nanwu uprising

216
00:09:53,380 --> 00:09:54,780
that began with his birth

217
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:56,060
has yet to be quelled.

218
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:59,660
With the Nightingale Division's shadow

219
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:01,900
creeping across Dazhou these past years,

220
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:04,060
his return will make him

221
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:06,540
the target of public criticism again.

222
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:09,140
However, Your Majesty,

223
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,660
the 7th Prince

224
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:12,540
has inherited your valor in battle,

225
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,820
leading the Chiyu Cavalry

226
00:10:13,820 --> 00:10:15,300
to countless victories.

227
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:17,940
Does this not prove

228
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:19,060
he is no foe

229
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:20,660
to the country?

230
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,300
It's not time yet.

231
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:28,020
I need to think about it.

232
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:36,620
Chief.

233
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,180
What are you looking at?

234
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:46,540
Go investigate the Directorate of Astronomy.

235
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:53,140
Haven't you

236
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:54,580
been reluctant to look into

237
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,540
what happened back then?

238
00:10:56,580 --> 00:10:57,700
I've changed my mind.

239
00:10:59,820 --> 00:11:01,020
I want to know

240
00:11:01,780 --> 00:11:03,820
who framed me.

241
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:10,620
Miss Chi,

242
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:12,380
this is the busiest street in town.

243
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:14,260
Yes.

244
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:15,660
Look at this shop, Miss Jiang.

245
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:17,060
It's been in business for years.

246
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:18,060
It's very famous.

247
00:11:18,060 --> 00:11:19,540
A snack spot up ahead is famous too.

248
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:22,140
Miss Chi, how's the location

249
00:11:22,140 --> 00:11:23,060
of this shop?

250
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:25,780
(Qiaoxiang Shop)
With so many shops around,

251
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:26,740
opening a shop here

252
00:11:26,740 --> 00:11:28,020
ensures a steady stream of customers.

253
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:29,820
I think so too.

254
00:11:30,180 --> 00:11:32,780
Once I get the shop up and running,

255
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:34,540
(Qiaoxiang Shop)
I'll need all hands on deck.

256
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:35,620
Miss Chi,

257
00:11:35,780 --> 00:11:37,780
I find you smart and resourceful.

258
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:39,940
Would you consider joining me?

259
00:11:40,420 --> 00:11:41,380
Miss Jiang,

260
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:43,060
you've already saved me from dire straits.

261
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,060
I don't know

262
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:45,180
how to repay you.

263
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:47,700
Now you extend another generous offer,

264
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:49,180
but I can't be in your debt.

265
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:51,500
What are your plans then?

266
00:11:52,060 --> 00:11:54,140
I plan to return home

267
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:56,300
and start a school in the countryside

268
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:58,460
to teach girls who cannot afford education

269
00:11:58,460 --> 00:11:59,540
literacy and reason.

270
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,060
I'll teach them not to be

271
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:02,420
as muddle-headed as I used to be.

272
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:04,780
I hope they will be like you,

273
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,380
who aspire to hearts holding vast horizons

274
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:07,940
and eyes perceiving greater justice.

275
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:08,780
I'm flattered.

276
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:10,540
Miss Chi,

277
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:13,060
your past sufferings are over.

278
00:12:13,820 --> 00:12:15,420
Every day

279
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:16,780
will be a new beginning.

280
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,020
Thank you, Miss Jiang.

281
00:12:19,930 --> 00:12:20,780
Take care.

282
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:25,460
(Qiaoxiang Shop)

283
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:26,580
Stay safe on the way.

284
00:12:33,420 --> 00:12:34,300
Miss Si.

