Let's go.

290
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:48,720
♪Ask the day and the night♪

291
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:52,320
♪If they saw a glimmer fall and take root♪

292
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:55,460
♪Growing between us♪

293
00:12:56,130 --> 00:13:01,130
♪And breeding love♪

294
00:13:02,470 --> 00:13:06,150
♪Smile at each other for the future♪

295
00:13:06,150 --> 00:13:09,710
♪In the end, we're still together♪

296
00:13:10,470 --> 00:13:12,130
♪Like shadows♪

297
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:15,780
Remember,

298
00:13:16,140 --> 00:13:18,020
Heaven helps those who help themselves

299
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:20,540
and abandons those who abandon themselves.

300
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:24,390
♪Our bond trickles down from youth♪

301
00:13:24,770 --> 00:13:26,550
♪Time glows♪

302
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:30,680
♪Together, we'll see light♪

303
00:13:31,110 --> 00:13:35,390
♪And stars♪

304
00:13:35,390 --> 00:13:41,180
(Morning Drizzle)

305
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:42,690
(Haitang Chamber)

306
00:13:42,700 --> 00:13:43,580
Father.

307
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:44,660
Si, you're home.

308
00:13:45,300 --> 00:13:46,140
Zhan.

309
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:49,420
Father,

310
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:50,900
what are you doing?

311
00:13:51,660 --> 00:13:52,780
Airing out books and paintings?

312
00:13:53,300 --> 00:13:54,660
I heard from your brother

313
00:13:54,780 --> 00:13:56,500
that you want to buy a shop.

314
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:00,300
Father,

315
00:14:00,380 --> 00:14:02,060
these are your lifelong collections.

316
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:03,580
How can you just pawn them off?

317
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:06,020
I'll find a way to buy the shop.

318
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:09,180
What can an unmarried girl like you

319
00:14:09,180 --> 00:14:11,060
possibly do?

320
00:14:11,060 --> 00:14:12,420
Father, here's my plan.

321
00:14:12,580 --> 00:14:13,540
I will

322
00:14:13,540 --> 00:14:14,580
rent the shop first.

323
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:15,900
It won't cost much.

324
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:17,460
Then I'll use

325
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,780
some of my dowry Mother left me,

326
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:19,700
and that should be enough.

327
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:21,580
Once the business picks up,

328
00:14:21,580 --> 00:14:22,900
I'll buy the shop.

329
00:14:23,140 --> 00:14:25,060
No renting. Buy it directly.

330
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,300
If my daughter wants to start a business,

331
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:28,940
shouldn't her father

332
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,300
buy her a shop?

333
00:14:30,300 --> 00:14:33,140
Keep the dowry your mother left you.

334
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:36,660
You need financial security to stand tall.

335
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:40,260
Besides, I just

336
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,660
followed rich young lords' trends

337
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:43,260
when buying these calligraphy works

338
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:44,420
and paintings.

339
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:46,060
I haven't

340
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:47,900
cared for them in years.

341
00:14:48,350 --> 00:14:49,660
Your brother's collections are even more

342
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:51,180
flashy without substance.

343
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:53,580
(Haitang Chamber)
He was excited for days

344
00:14:53,940 --> 00:14:55,540
and then threw them in the study

345
00:14:55,540 --> 00:14:56,850
without even looking at them for years.

346
00:14:56,850 --> 00:14:58,580
Look at this dust!

347
00:14:58,700 --> 00:14:59,540
Exactly.

348
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:00,940
Before buying,

349
00:15:00,940 --> 00:15:02,540
they seemed like rare treasures;

350
00:15:02,700 --> 00:15:03,820
once home,

351
00:15:04,300 --> 00:15:05,380
just some trinkets.

352
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:08,180
Si, do me a favor.

353
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:09,060
You know what,

354
00:15:09,060 --> 00:15:10,940
my study is a mess and can barely squeeze in.

355
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:12,140
Zhan,

356
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:13,780
Father.

357
00:15:14,060 --> 00:15:16,420
Enough, come help now.

358
00:15:16,700 --> 00:15:18,300
Your brother is clumsy.

359
00:15:18,300 --> 00:15:19,540
If he breaks anything,

360
00:15:19,780 --> 00:15:21,380
we won't get a good price.

361
00:15:21,660 --> 00:15:22,500
Father,

362
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:25,380
are you really that sure

363
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:27,580
I can run this shop well?

364
00:15:27,700 --> 00:15:29,140
Of course.

365
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:30,300
Don't forget

366
00:15:30,420 --> 00:15:33,420
your grandpa was Lingshui's richest man.

367
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,060
Business sense

368
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:36,460
is an inherited gift

369
00:15:36,460 --> 00:15:38,380
in your bloodline.

370
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:39,500
Father,

371
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:42,180
all I do is eat, drink, and be merry.

372
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:43,260
So my blood of mine

373
00:15:43,260 --> 00:15:44,420
must have come from you, right?

374
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:45,260
Scram.

375
00:15:45,540 --> 00:15:46,780
Didn't I tell you

376
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:48,420
I picked you up from somewhere?

377
00:15:49,660 --> 00:15:50,700
Seriously?

378
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:52,660
No wonder you've been so awful to me.

379
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:54,180
By the way, Si,

380
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:56,900
you mustn't let your grandma

381
00:15:56,900 --> 00:15:58,940
find out about your business venture.

382
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:01,060
Like most Ling'an folk,

383
00:16:01,060 --> 00:16:02,180
she looks down

384
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:04,420
on merchants,

385
00:16:04,700 --> 00:16:05,900
and would never allow the Earl's

386
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,900
legitimate daughter to engage in trade.

387
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:08,900
Understood?

388
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:11,500
I understand.

389
00:16:17,260 --> 00:16:18,100
Father,

390
00:16:18,260 --> 00:16:19,900
see how effective

391
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,180
this Yunxiang Herb is.

392
00:16:21,540 --> 00:16:23,380
The books

393
00:16:23,380 --> 00:16:24,420
show no insect damage

394
00:16:24,420 --> 00:16:25,580
after a full year,

395
00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:26,420
still perfectly intact.

396
00:16:27,140 --> 00:16:29,500
My daughter knows so much.

397
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:33,300
By the way, Father,

398
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:35,580
I've rarely heard you mention

399
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:37,020
the Directorate of Astronomy.

400
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:38,780
And you seldom associate

401
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:40,300
with your former colleagues either.

402
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:43,060
Since your mother's passing,

403
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:45,260
I've lost the heart for official duties,

404
00:16:46,060 --> 00:16:48,380
so I resigned from my post.

405
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:50,300
I've always thought

406
00:16:50,420 --> 00:16:51,900
reading the night skies

407
00:16:52,140 --> 00:16:53,180
is mysterious,

408
00:16:54,060 --> 00:16:55,300
predicting weather

409
00:16:55,540 --> 00:16:56,820
and divining fortunes.

410
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:59,540
While celestial study

411
00:16:59,940 --> 00:17:02,300
holds endless wonders,

412
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:05,060
the Directorate of Astronomy

413
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,700
is not just about astronomy and geography.

414
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:10,500
There are more

415
00:17:10,900 --> 00:17:12,780
social climbers

416
00:17:13,420 --> 00:17:15,540
and forced compromises.

417
00:17:15,740 --> 00:17:16,580
Father,

418
00:17:18,210 --> 00:17:19,220
do you recall those copybooks

419
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:21,540
you kept drilling me on as a child?

420
00:17:21,860 --> 00:17:22,700
Look,

421
00:17:22,940 --> 00:17:24,620
this one slipped through the cracks.

422
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:26,860
I vividly recall these copybooks.

423
00:17:27,540 --> 00:17:28,380
Back then,

424
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:29,980
every time I bought one,

425
00:17:29,980 --> 00:17:31,740
it would go missing.

426
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:33,220
It was strange.

427
00:17:34,460 --> 00:17:35,860
I threw them all away secretly.

428
00:17:35,860 --> 00:17:37,220
I threw a lot away for you.

429
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:38,460
No wonder your handwriting

430
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:40,100
is pure chicken scratch.

431
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:41,460
This isn't for sale.

432
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:42,540
Drill those strokes.

433
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:44,260
No, I'll sell this one first.

434
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:45,420
Ji, hurry up.

435
00:17:45,420 --> 00:17:47,020
- Sell this copybook first!
- Stop there!

436
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:48,100
You can't sell it.

437
00:17:48,100 --> 00:17:49,020
If you sell it,

438
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:51,100
you'll face month-long house arrest.

439
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:51,940
Don't sell it!

440
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,060
Stop right there!

441
00:17:58,140 --> 00:18:00,020
(Fragrance Shop)

442
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:00,860
Miss,

443
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:01,980
no one is willing

444
00:18:01,980 --> 00:18:03,600
(Fragrance Shop)
to come and help in our shop.

445
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:05,100
Ling'an women all balk

446
00:18:05,100 --> 00:18:06,780
at being called businesswomen.

447
00:18:07,500 --> 00:18:08,980
The opening day is looming,

448
00:18:09,100 --> 00:18:10,500
but we're still short of staff.

449
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:11,740
What should we do?

450
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:13,980
Miss Chuchu!

451
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:15,540
Chuchu.

452
00:18:15,540 --> 00:18:16,620
Jiang Zhan told me

453
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:17,460
you're hiring,

454
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:19,660
so I brought a candidate.

455
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:20,860
(Rou'er)
Miss Jiang, how do you do?

456
00:18:20,860 --> 00:18:22,260
Miss Jiang, congratulations

457
00:18:22,260 --> 00:18:23,180
on your new shop's opening.

458
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:24,260
How do you do?

459
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:25,740
Chuchu,

460
00:18:25,740 --> 00:18:27,540
you've truly saved me in my hour of need.

461
00:18:27,540 --> 00:18:29,620
Rest assured, Rou'er is definitely reliable.

462
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:31,180
She's from my hometown,

463
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:33,020
once a rouge shop owner herself.

464
00:18:33,820 --> 00:18:36,140
Chief, after cracking the case

465
00:18:36,140 --> 00:18:37,500
with His Majesty's backing,

466
00:18:37,500 --> 00:18:39,300
sycophants are eager to curry favor with us.

467
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:41,620
Mr. Zhao from the Grand Council...

468
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:42,460
No. I'm busy.

469
00:18:42,690 --> 00:18:43,530
Yes.

470
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:44,430
Mr. Yu.

471
00:18:44,540 --> 00:18:45,660
- Mr. Jiang.
- What a coincidence.

472
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:47,540
- Are you rich?
- Come on.

473
00:18:47,540 --> 00:18:48,700
You bought so much stuff.

474
00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:50,480
My sister's fragrance shop

475
00:18:50,480 --> 00:18:51,420
opens the day after tomorrow.

476
00:18:51,430 --> 00:18:52,480
I bought her some opening gifts.

477
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,540
Fragrance shop?

478
00:18:54,180 --> 00:18:55,460
Perfect timing.

479
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:57,700
I was going to deliver your invitation.

480
00:18:57,820 --> 00:18:59,660
Be sure to come support the opening.

481
00:18:59,660 --> 00:19:01,660
I'm sorry, but he isn't available that day.

482
00:19:01,660 --> 00:19:02,500
I am.

483
00:19:03,180 --> 00:19:04,740
I'll adjust my schedule.

484
00:19:04,740 --> 00:19:05,580
I'll come, definitely.

485
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:06,500
That's good.

486
00:19:06,740 --> 00:19:07,860
Fragrance Shop?

487
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:09,300
Good name.

488
00:19:19,820 --> 00:19:20,660
Long Dan!

489
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:23,580
Long Dan!

490
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:26,180
What's up, sir?

491
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:27,420
Where did you put it?

492
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:28,700
Where did I put what?

493
00:19:29,150 --> 00:19:30,100
Where did you put the thing

494
00:19:30,100 --> 00:19:31,060
I asked you to get?

495
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:32,420
You didn't ask me to get anything.

496
00:19:32,900 --> 00:19:34,060
Where's my bronze mirror?

497
00:19:34,060 --> 00:19:35,300
Where did you put it?

498
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:36,780
We don't have a bronze mirror.

499
00:19:38,340 --> 00:19:39,580
Go borrow one from the neighbor.

500
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,020
- Go, go, go!
- I have to...

501
00:20:06,860 --> 00:20:07,780
Chief. Chief.

502
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:08,940
Mirror, mirror.

503
00:20:09,340 --> 00:20:10,180
The mirror is here.

504
00:20:12,380 --> 00:20:13,780
- Take it easy.
- Here.

505
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:24,980
Chief, you're dressed like this

506
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:27,020
to meet Miss Jiang?

507
00:20:27,900 --> 00:20:28,740
What do you think?

508
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:30,420
With such...

509
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:35,020
With such striking poise,

510
00:20:35,020 --> 00:20:36,100
you're sure

511
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:37,260
to impress her.

512
00:20:40,060 --> 00:20:41,260
Haven't I always been like this?

513
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:43,140
Sure, sure.

514
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:46,020
Ring the gong, prosper the business.

515
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:48,220
Grand opening,

516
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:51,540
great fortune.

517
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:54,580
Mirror the heart for clarity.

518
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:57,570
Act with integrity, discipline strictly.

519
00:21:02,740 --> 00:21:04,140
Subtle scents through seasons;

520
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,700
fragrant trails on every journey.

521
00:21:06,580 --> 00:21:07,860
Gourds displayed,

522
00:21:07,860 --> 00:21:09,020
fortune conveyed.

523
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:10,660
New business, thriving fortunes.

524
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:14,260
Look how handsome

525
00:21:14,260 --> 00:21:15,140
those gentlemen are.

526
00:21:15,140 --> 00:21:17,460
Mr. Yu, not bad.

527
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:20,060
You look dashing today.

528
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:23,940
- Mr. Zhen, thank you for coming.
- Jiang...

529
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:24,780
Thank you.

530
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:28,900
Mr. Zhen, don't you always advocate

531
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:31,100
unwavering duty

532
00:21:31,100 --> 00:21:33,220
and attendance on official leave?

533
00:21:34,180 --> 00:21:35,020
Yes.

534
00:21:35,260 --> 00:21:37,300
But Miss Jiang

535
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:38,660
personally delivered the invitation

536
00:21:38,660 --> 00:21:39,980
to my door yesterday.

537
00:21:40,580 --> 00:21:41,940
With such an honor,

538
00:21:42,100 --> 00:21:43,180
you know I can't possibly decline.

539
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:44,220
Thanks a lot.

540
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:45,500
Really?

541
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:47,140
Why?

542
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:48,780
Didn't you receive

543
00:21:48,780 --> 00:21:49,980
Miss Jiang's invitation?

544
00:21:50,180 --> 00:21:51,500
Of course I did.

545
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:52,940
That's why I'm here.

546
00:21:53,940 --> 00:21:55,260
Before she had the chance to deliver it,

547
00:21:55,260 --> 00:21:57,540
we happened to meet on the road,

548
00:21:57,540 --> 00:21:58,860
so it saved her the trouble

549
00:21:58,860 --> 00:22:00,020
of making a trip.

550
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:01,700
I see.

551
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:02,980
What a coincidence.

552
00:22:03,820 --> 00:22:05,460
Chief, didn't you say Jiang Zhan...

553
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,720
Miss Jiang, prepare for the unveiling.

554
00:22:12,220 --> 00:22:13,140
(Fragrance Shop)

555
00:22:13,140 --> 00:22:15,420
Great!

556
00:22:15,420 --> 00:22:17,260
- Great!
- Bravo!

557
00:22:20,420 --> 00:22:24,060
Share fragrance, gather blessings.

558
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:26,940
Perfect!

559
00:22:27,300 --> 00:22:28,860
Here, one for each.

560
00:22:28,860 --> 00:22:30,300
- It's all inside.
- Take a look inside.

561
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:31,500
Come in and take a look.

562
00:22:31,820 --> 00:22:33,180
Thanks for coming and supporting us.

563
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:34,340
Come on inside.

564
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:35,180
Have a look inside.

565
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:36,580
- Come on.
- One for each.

566
00:22:36,580 --> 00:22:37,740
Is this yours?

567
00:22:38,140 --> 00:22:39,340
- Thanks.
- Thanks a lot.

568
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:40,540
Have a look inside, guys.

569
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:41,700
Come on.

570
00:22:41,940 --> 00:22:43,300
- Si.
- Have a look inside.

571
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:44,580
- Si.
- Come on in.

572
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:46,670
Good luck with your business.

573
00:22:46,670 --> 00:22:47,940
(Wealth from all directions)
Come on in.

574
00:22:48,500 --> 00:22:49,460
Thanks, Zhan.

575
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:50,700
Miss Jiang.

576
00:22:51,340 --> 00:22:53,220
Congratulations on your opening.

577
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:55,500
(Auspicious opening, customers surge)

578
00:22:56,100 --> 00:22:57,180
Thanks, Mr. Zhen.

579
00:22:58,580 --> 00:22:59,420
Miss Jiang!

580
00:23:00,100 --> 00:23:01,500
May your business thrive and prosper.

581
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,060
